title: 5 dollar starter pack
body: Does the 5 dollar starter pack card give you RP?{{champion:74}}

replies.body:
Hey there,

The $5 starter pack will give you the following;

* 5 Champions
  * Annie
  * Ashe
  * Ryze
  * Garen
  * Master Yi
* 1 Skin
  * Assassin Master Yi
* Boosts
   * 7 Day XP Boost
   * 1 Day IP Boost
